metadata.name: Layne the Nihon Warrior
metadata.description:
Unofficial comic book about G.U. #9761, created by Sygo, OG holder, Lore Core and AV Core Council member of Genuine Undead.

Barely coping with his frenetic life through a near future dystopian Tokyo, in the year 2047, Layne soon will found himself involved in things far bigger than him, and he will be pushed to the edge. 

You don't choose G.U., it's G.U. that chooses you.

10% of all income will go to the Genuine Undead community wallet as a form of respect to the original art and the awesome Community.
